item.description:
It's looking like a beautiful friday evening and a nice time to be outdoors. Join me over at Chucksters for a round of Mini golf. Located in Chichester NH, Chucksters has the most challenging course I've played in the area, not to mention the longest hole.

Each round is only $8. If you want more they have batting cages , go carts, a climbing wall and good ice cream !

So lets have some fun and tap some little balls around the greens. Check it out !

http://www.chucksters.com/golf.php

My number 603-315-0275
